name: JF-01 Vintage Overdrive
details:
OverdriveA representation of the classic Tube Screamer, with a RC4558 chip. The overdrive effect is mellow, mild, smooth--simply exquisite! Also nice sustain.
True bypass design minimizes tone loss.
Aluminum alloy casing with stoving varnish finish.
